data.description: A quaint cottage sitting on an acre with well and irrigation for watering.  Updated with an upper primary bedroom and beautiful bathroom.  There's a bonus loft type area for office space or a TV room.  The main level has beautiful hardwood floors with 2 small bedrooms and bath.  Nice open living/dining area with hardwood floors and an updated kitchen with painted cabinets, stainless appls and a stackable washer/dryer.  There are 2 storage sheds, extra parking and a beautiful country setting.
